{
  "stem": "21786.8",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Compared what preceded, you know, we got a little bit more food, not that it would be something where you would have to keep a diet.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, the hygienic conditions were a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And being young, you simply shed the memory of the horror of Auschwitz relatively quickly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, for instance, we really, every morning, were permitted to wash, not that there would be any hot water.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the winter was not so drastic, and the-- so that we had enough water.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were warned that there will be bombardments of the factory, that we will have to be very quick to evacuate, which will be permitted.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were not permitted to go to the shelters like the civilian population.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Also, the latrines were-- simply saw that they were kept clean.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were only men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, I forgot to mention in Auschwitz that that was one of the great humiliations, which in the end, somehow culminated in indifference, for there were a huge space of cement, kind of huge blocks with round holes in it, where were sitting men and women together.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then later somebody achieved even that they put some kind of a divider, the jute bags, so that you didn't see the face always, but you just see the rest of the body.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But at that point certainly, nobody minded, for we had been so decimated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- I call it dehumanized-- that simply didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Here it was a clean proposition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mentioned there how we started to wash the laundry for the SS men, which kept many of us alive, for I succeeded always to get something for it.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
